The paper investigates the usage of a camera glasses product, which involves human-computer interaction (HCI) and multimedia (MM) aspects. The study also explores the social and individual factors that influence the use of the product, which relates to the categories of cybernetics (CY), social and information networks (SI), and other (OH).
